{
  "video_id": "izddjAp_N4I",
  "title": "David Bismark: E-voting without fraud",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 16260.000000000002,
      "end_time": 18260.0,
      "text": "So there are a few things"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18260.0,
      "end_time": 21260.0,
      "text": "that bring us humans together in the way that an election does."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21260.0,
      "end_time": 24260.0,
      "text": "We stand in elections; we vote in elections;"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24260.0,
      "end_time": 26260.0,
      "text": "we observe elections."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26260.0,
      "end_time": 29260.0,
      "text": "Our democracies rely on elections."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29260.0,
      "end_time": 32260.0,
      "text": "We all understand why we have elections,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32259.0,
      "end_time": 34260.0,
      "text": "and we all leave the house on the same day"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34260.0,
      "end_time": 36260.0,
      "text": "to go and vote."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36260.0,
      "end_time": 39260.0,
      "text": "We cherish the opportunity to have our say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39260.0,
      "end_time": 42260.0,
      "text": "to help decide the future of the country."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 44260.0,
      "end_time": 46260.0,
      "text": "The fundamental idea is that politicians"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 46260.0,
      "end_time": 49260.0,
      "text": "are given mandate to speak for us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 49260.0,
      "end_time": 51260.0,
      "text": "to make decisions on our behalf"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51260.0,
      "end_time": 53260.0,
      "text": "that affect us all."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53260.0,
      "end_time": 56260.0,
      "text": "Without that mandate, they would be corrupt."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 56260.0,
      "end_time": 58260.0,
      "text": "Well unfortunately, power corrupts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 58260.0,
      "end_time": 61260.0,
      "text": "and so people will do lots of things"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 61260.0,
      "end_time": 64259.0,
      "text": "to get power and to stay in power,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 64260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67260.0,
      "text": "including doing bad things to elections."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 68260.0,
      "end_time": 70260.0,
      "text": "You see, even if the idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 70260.0,
      "end_time": 72260.0,
      "text": "of the election is perfect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 72260.0,
      "end_time": 75260.0,
      "text": "running a countrywide election is a big project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 75260.0,
      "end_time": 78260.0,
      "text": "and big projects are messy."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 78260.0,
      "end_time": 80260.0,
      "text": "Whenever there is an election,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 80260.0,
      "end_time": 82260.0,
      "text": "it seems like something always goes wrong,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 82260.0,
      "end_time": 84260.0,
      "text": "someone tries to cheat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 84260.0,
      "end_time": 87260.0,
      "text": "or something goes accidentally awry --"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 87260.0,
      "end_time": 90260.0,
      "text": "a ballot box goes missing here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 90260.0,
      "end_time": 93260.0,
      "text": "chads are left hanging over here."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 93260.0,
      "end_time": 97260.0,
      "text": "To make sure as few things as possible go wrong,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 97260.0,
      "end_time": 100260.0,
      "text": "we have all these procedures around the election."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 100260.0,
      "end_time": 103260.0,
      "text": "So for example, you come to the polling station,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 103260.0,
      "end_time": 106260.0,
      "text": "and a poll station worker asks for your ID"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 106260.0,
      "end_time": 108260.0,
      "text": "before giving you a ballot form"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 108260.0,
      "end_time": 110260.0,
      "text": "and asking you to go into a voting booth"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 110260.0,
      "end_time": 112260.0,
      "text": "to fill out your vote."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 112260.0,
      "end_time": 114260.0,
      "text": "When you come back out, you get to drop your vote"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 114260.0,
      "end_time": 116260.0,
      "text": "into the ballot box"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 116260.0,
      "end_time": 118260.0,
      "text": "where it mixes with all the other votes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 118260.0,
      "end_time": 121260.0,
      "text": "so that no one knows how you voted."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 121260.0,
      "end_time": 123260.0,
      "text": "Well, what I want us to think about for a moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 123260.0,
      "end_time": 125260.0,
      "text": "is what happens after that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 125260.0,
      "end_time": 127260.0,
      "text": "after you drop your vote into the ballot box."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 127260.0,
      "end_time": 129259.0,
      "text": "And most people would go home"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 129258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131260.0,
      "text": "and feel sure that their vote has been counted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 131260.0,
      "end_time": 133260.0,
      "text": "because they trust"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 133260.0,
      "end_time": 135260.0,
      "text": "that the election system works."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 135260.0,
      "end_time": 138260.0,
      "text": "They trust that election workers and election observers"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 138260.0,
      "end_time": 141260.0,
      "text": "do their jobs and do their jobs correctly."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 142260.0,
      "end_time": 145260.0,
      "text": "The ballot boxes go to counting places."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 145260.0,
      "end_time": 148260.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re unsealed and the votes are poured out"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 148260.0,
      "end_time": 151260.0,
      "text": "and laboriously counted."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 151260.0,
      "end_time": 153260.0,
      "text": "Most of us have to trust"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 153260.0,
      "end_time": 155260.0,
      "text": "that that happens correctly for our own vote,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 155260.0,
      "end_time": 158260.0,
      "text": "and we all have to trust that that happens correctly"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 158260.0,
      "end_time": 161260.0,
      "text": "for all the votes in the election."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 161260.0,
      "end_time": 164260.0,
      "text": "So we have to trust a lot of people."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 165260.0,
      "end_time": 168260.0,
      "text": "We have to trust a lot of procedures."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 169260.0,
      "end_time": 172260.0,
      "text": "And sometimes we even have to trust computers."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 174260.0,
      "end_time": 176260.0,
      "text": "So imagine hundreds of millions of voters"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 176260.0,
      "end_time": 178260.0,
      "text": "casting hundreds of millions of votes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 178260.0,
      "end_time": 181260.0,
      "text": "all to be counted correctly"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 181260.0,
      "end_time": 184260.0,
      "text": "and all the things that can possibly go wrong"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 184260.0,
      "end_time": 187260.0,
      "text": "causing all these bad headlines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 189260.0,
      "end_time": 192260.0,
      "text": "and you cannot help but feel exhausted at the idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 192260.0,
      "end_time": 195260.0,
      "text": "of trying to make elections better."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 198260.0,
      "end_time": 200260.0,
      "text": "Well in the face of all these bad headlines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 200260.0,
      "end_time": 203260.0,
      "text": "researchers have taken a step back"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 203260.0,
      "end_time": 206260.0,
      "text": "and thought about how we can do elections differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 207260.0,
      "end_time": 210260.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ve zoomed out and looked at the big picture."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 210260.0,
      "end_time": 212260.0,
      "text": "And the big picture is this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 212260.0,
      "end_time": 215260.0,
      "text": "elections should be verifiable."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 216260.0,
      "end_time": 219260.0,
      "text": "Voters should be able to check"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 219260.0,
      "end_time": 222260.0,
      "text": "that their votes are counted correctly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 222260.0,
      "end_time": 224260.0,
      "text": "without breaking election secrecy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 224260.0,
      "end_time": 227260.0,
      "text": "which is so very important."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 227260.0,
      "end_time": 229260.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s the tough part."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 229260.0,
      "end_time": 232260.0,
      "text": "How do we make an election system completely verifiable"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 232260.0,
      "end_time": 234260.0,
      "text": "while keeping the votes"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 234260.0,
      "end_time": 236260.0,
      "text": "absolutely secret?"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 236260.0,
      "end_time": 238260.0,
      "text": "Well, the way we&#39;ve come up with"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 238260.0,
      "end_time": 240260.0,
      "text": "uses computers"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 240260.0,
      "end_time": 242260.0,
      "text": "but doesn&#39;t depend on them."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 242260.0,
      "end_time": 244260.0,
      "text": "And the secret is the ballot form."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 244260.0,
      "end_time": 246260.0,
      "text": "And if you look closely at these ballot forms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 246260.0,
      "end_time": 248260.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll notice that the candidate list"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 248260.0,
      "end_time": 250260.0,
      "text": "is in a different order on each one."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 250260.0,
      "end_time": 253260.0,
      "text": "And that means, if you mark your choices on one of them"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 253260.0,
      "end_time": 255260.0,
      "text": "and then remove the candidate list,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 255260.0,
      "end_time": 258260.0,
      "text": "I won&#39;t be able to tell from the bit remaining"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 258260.0,
      "end_time": 261260.0,
      "text": "what your vote is for."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 261260.0,
      "end_time": 264260.0,
      "text": "And on each ballot form there is this encrypted value"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 264260.0,
      "end_time": 266260.0,
      "text": "in the form of this 2D barcode"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 266260.0,
      "end_time": 268260.0,
      "text": "on the right."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 268260.0,
      "end_time": 270260.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s some complicated cryptography"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 270260.0,
      "end_time": 272260.0,
      "text": "going on in there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 272260.0,
      "end_time": 274260.0,
      "text": "but what&#39;s not complicated"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 274260.0,
      "end_time": 277260.0,
      "text": "is voting with one of these forms."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 277260.0,
      "end_time": 280260.0,
      "text": "So we can let computers do all the complicated cryptography for us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 280260.0,
      "end_time": 283260.0,
      "text": "and then we&#39;ll use the paper for verification."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 284260.0,
      "end_time": 286260.0,
      "text": "So this is how you vote."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 286260.0,
      "end_time": 290260.0,
      "text": "You get one of these ballot forms at random,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 290260.0,
      "end_time": 292260.0,
      "text": "and then you go into the voting booth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 292260.0,
      "end_time": 294260.0,
      "text": "and you mark your choices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 294260.0,
      "end_time": 297260.0,
      "text": "and you tear along a perforation."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 299260.0,
      "end_time": 302260.0,
      "text": "And you shred the candidate list."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 302260.0,
      "end_time": 305260.0,
      "text": "And the bit that remains, the one with your marks --"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 305260.0,
      "end_time": 307260.0,
      "text": "this is your encrypted vote."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 307260.0,
      "end_time": 309260.0,
      "text": "So you let a poll station worker"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 309260.0,
      "end_time": 311260.0,
      "text": "scan your encrypted vote."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 311260.0,
      "end_time": 313260.0,
      "text": "And because it&#39;s encrypted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 313260.0,
      "end_time": 315260.0,
      "text": "it can be submitted, stored"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 315260.0,
      "end_time": 318260.0,
      "text": "and counted centrally"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 318260.0,
      "end_time": 320260.0,
      "text": "and displayed on a website"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 320260.0,
      "end_time": 323260.0,
      "text": "for anyone to see, including you."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 323260.0,
      "end_time": 326260.0,
      "text": "So you take this encrypted vote"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 326260.0,
      "end_time": 328260.0,
      "text": "home as your receipt."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 328260.0,
      "end_time": 330260.0,
      "text": "And after the close of the election,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 330260.0,
      "end_time": 332260.0,
      "text": "you can check that your vote was counted"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 332260.0,
      "end_time": 335260.0,
      "text": "by comparing your receipt"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 335260.0,
      "end_time": 338260.0,
      "text": "to the vote on the website."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 339260.0,
      "end_time": 341260.0,
      "text": "And remember, the vote is encrypted"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 341260.0,
      "end_time": 344260.0,
      "text": "from the moment you leave the voting booth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 344260.0,
      "end_time": 347260.0,
      "text": "so if an election official wants to find out how you voted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 347260.0,
      "end_time": 349260.0,
      "text": "they will not be able to."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 349260.0,
      "end_time": 351260.0,
      "text": "If the government wants to find out how you voted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 351260.0,
      "end_time": 354260.0,
      "text": "they won&#39;t be able to."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 354260.0,
      "end_time": 356260.0,
      "text": "No hacker can break in"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 356260.0,
      "end_time": 358260.0,
      "text": "and find out how you voted."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 358260.0,
      "end_time": 361260.0,
      "text": "No hacker can break in and change your vote,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 361260.0,
      "end_time": 364260.0,
      "text": "because then it won&#39;t match your receipt."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 364260.0,
      "end_time": 367260.0,
      "text": "Votes can&#39;t go missing"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 367260.0,
      "end_time": 370260.0,
      "text": "because then you won&#39;t find yours when you look for it."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 371260.0,
      "end_time": 374260.0,
      "text": "But the election magic doesn&#39;t stop there."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 374260.0,
      "end_time": 376260.0,
      "text": "Instead, we want to make the whole process"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 376260.0,
      "end_time": 378260.0,
      "text": "so transparent"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 378260.0,
      "end_time": 381260.0,
      "text": "that news media and international observers"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 381260.0,
      "end_time": 383260.0,
      "text": "and anyone who wants to"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 383260.0,
      "end_time": 385260.0,
      "text": "can download all the election data"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 385260.0,
      "end_time": 387260.0,
      "text": "and do the count themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 387260.0,
      "end_time": 390260.0,
      "text": "They can check that all the votes were counted correctly."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 390260.0,
      "end_time": 392260.0,
      "text": "They can check"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 392260.0,
      "end_time": 394260.0,
      "text": "that the announced result of the election"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 394260.0,
      "end_time": 396260.0,
      "text": "is the correct one."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 396260.0,
      "end_time": 398260.0,
      "text": "And these are elections"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 398260.0,
      "end_time": 400260.0,
      "text": "by the people, for the people."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 400260.0,
      "end_time": 403260.0,
      "text": "So the next step for our democracies"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 403260.0,
      "end_time": 405260.0,
      "text": "are transparent"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 405260.0,
      "end_time": 407260.0,
      "text": "and verifiable elections."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 407260.0,
      "end_time": 409260.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 409260.0,
      "end_time": 416260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
